  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will help us learn how a child's diet affects growth and development.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This study will see how infants diet affects their growth and development. Up to 60 infants
      will be enrolled for one visit.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
