    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        Infants
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Exclusive breast feeding or cow milk formula feeding during the first 3 months of
             life.

          -  For formula feeders, exclusively on Similac Advance Formula for at least 1 month prior
             to visit

          -  Age 2.5-3.5 months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Infants born to mother with preexisting medical conditions.

          -  Infants born to mother with medications during pregnancy known to influence fetal
             growth.

          -  Infants born to smoking, alcohol drinking or drug use mothers during pregnancy.

          -  Preterm
      </textblock>
